# Mkondo — User Flows

Operator and applicant flows.

---

## Operator Flow — First Time

```text
OPERATOR LOGS INTO MKONDO
    │
    ▼
[ Step 1 ] PROGRAM INFO FORM
    │   ├── Program name
    │   ├── Ecosystem / chain
    │   ├── Focus area and vertical
    │   ├── Eligibility criteria
    │   └── Rubric selection
    │
    ▼
[ Step 2 ] PROGRAM ROUND INTENT FORM
    │   ├── Round details
    │   ├── Budget and dates
    │   ├── Target applicants
    │   ├── Program metrics
    │   ├── Application form selection
    │   └── Rubric selection
    │
    ▼
[ Step 3 ] CONFIGURE APPLICATION FORM
    │   ├── Load form template
    │   ├── Adjust fields
    │   └── Mark required fields
    │
    ▼
[ Step 4 ] CONFIGURE RUBRIC
    │   ├── Add criteria
    │   ├── Set score range
    │   └── Set weights
    │
    ▼
[ Step 5 ] REVIEW & PUBLISH
    │   └── Public application page generated
    │
    ▼
PROGRAM GOES LIVE
```

---

## Operator Flow — Returning (New Round)

```text
OPERATOR OPENS EXISTING PROGRAM
    │
    ▼
[ Step 1 ] REVIEW PROGRAM INFO
    │   └── Update core details if needed
    │
    ▼
[ Step 2 ] UPDATE ROUND INTENT
    │   ├── Update dates, budget, goals, and metrics
    │   ├── Reuse or update application form
    │   └── Reuse or update rubric
    │
    ▼
[ Step 3 ] REVIEW & PUBLISH
    │   └── New round goes live
```

---

## Applicant Flow — Public, No Login

```text
APPLICANT OPENS PUBLIC APPLICATION PAGE
    │
    ▼
PROGRAM PAGE
    │   ├── Program overview
    │   ├── Eligibility requirements
    │   ├── Funding scope
    │   └── Apply entry point
    │
    ▼
PRE-SCREENING
    │   ├── Basic fit questions
    │   └── Eligibility check
    │
    ▼
FULL APPLICATION FORM
    │   ├── Project details
    │   ├── Team and links
    │   ├── Funding request
    │   └── Milestones and supporting information
    │
    ▼
SUBMISSION CONFIRMATION
    │   └── Application recorded
```

---

## Operator Review Flow

```text
APPLICATIONS QUEUE
    │   ├── Applications organized for review
    │   └── Screening result surfaced before full review
    │
    ▼
APPLICATION DETAIL
    │   ├── Full application content
    │   └── Evaluation summary
    │
    ▼
DECISION
    ├── APPROVE
    ├── REJECT
    └── REQUEST INFO
    │
    ▼
REGISTRY UPDATED
```
